title: Join GTA+
headline: Join GTA+
subtitle: Get 2X GTA$ & RP on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales
content:
Join Grand Theft Auto Online’s premium Membership program this month and you’ll receive 2X rewards on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales.

You can also get 50% off Auto Shop Properties, 50% off Drift Tuning Upgrades, and an Atomic Racing Bomber and Cap.

GTA+ automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
